22
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:58,351
No!

23
00:00:58,351 --> 00:00:58,918
You can't!

24
00:00:58,933 --> 00:00:59,974
Don't blame me!

25
00:00:59,974 --> 00:01:01,141
Every year on this date,

26
00:01:01,141 --> 00:01:02,813
