27
00:01:03,399 --> 00:01:05,202
I'll burn 10 billion for you!

28
00:01:08,433 --> 00:01:09,859
I even had his child.

29
00:01:09,859 --> 00:01:10,476
Hahaha...

30
00:01:12,766 --> 00:01:13,502
