46
00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:43,371
Hey, hey, Kun!

47
00:01:43,371 --> 00:01:44,311
There you are!

48
00:01:44,311 --> 00:01:45,664
Let's go fishing in the lake.

49
00:01:46,466 --> 00:01:47,225
Sounds good.

50
00:01:47,225 --> 00:01:49,108
I've always heard the fish in this lake are

51
